oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Coffee County road construction
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of road paving done by Summitville Sand and Gravel. This photograph was taken after one mile of pavement had been completed. Workers, horses, wagons, and pieces of stone are seen.
